{"tid":1427684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於輿論戰 有啲野我地可以做得聰明啲","createTime":"2019-08-07T07:20:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T10:58:03.000Z","uid":104507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"77b44aeb7cf5e568d79fbbea91bb3bfbb43b6e0b","tid":1427684,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:20:48.000Z","msg":"睇返黑警最近兩日嘅小動作<br />\n知道輿論戰又一觸即發<br />\n<br />\n如果發生任何爭執或衝突<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">要有手足即刻變身&quot;記者&quot;</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">確保有人紀錄低事件嘅前因後果</span></span><br />\n減低只有片面影片流出 送材料比對家<br />\n因為我相信大家唔會無差別攻擊市民<br />\n所以大家一定要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">出師有名 搶對家道德高底</span></span><br />\n<br />\n出到嚟嘅各位手足<br />\n無論我地內心嬲到猶如洪水猛獸<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係鏡頭面前一定要做返雞蛋 做柔弱嘅一方</span></span><br />\n和理非、爸爸媽媽會更有理據繼續支持同&quot;守護孩子&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">玩火無問題 但一定要對準玩</span></span><br />\n例如 垃圾❎ 宿舍❎ 路過TK車、市民❎<br />\n火魔法✅ 警局✅ 黑警✅ 黑社會✅<br />\n<br />\n最近紅媒開始對準嚟製造輿論<br />\n而好多淺黃無可避免會動搖咗<br />\n無可否認 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">對家製造輿論同文宣有一手</span></span><br />\n我地更要向對家學習 <span style=\"color: orange;\">打對等輿論戰 製造對等文宣</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">將文宣同輿論打入藍色區域<br />\n脫離同溫層</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ha9MS6k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHa9MS6k.png&h=9f733659&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"2bcd3a40055d4da5b1c7966243a46c309b27c1ed","tid":1427684,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:24:28.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"8038e6af7e24e83716692d9bee9006f627ba19f7","tid":1427684,"uid":284636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:58:03.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"}]}